Simple Explanation

Start the system.

Arduino generates a random number (1–10).

User enters a guess using keypad/buttons.

Arduino compares the guess with the random number.

If correct → show Correct (LED/LCD).

If guess is higher → show Lower.

If guess is lower → show Higher.

User guesses again until correct.

End.

